parameters:
\N<Young Man>S-stop it! What are you doing to my sister! Are you guys out
of your minds, taking that guy's words seriously!?

\N<Man>Shut up! If we don't do this, we're all going to hell
anyway! Just hand over the girl quietly!

\N<Man>Protective armor can be considered the bare minimum of
preparation, whether exploring ruins or fighting in the
training grounds.

\N<Man>Segi-san, where do you think you're going? I have a bad
feeling about this, but if you're planning to go to the
ruins ahead, I'd advise against it.

\N<Man>Even the entrance management of the ruins that have been in
this town for ages is now handled by Luda's soldiers...

\N<Man>There are still factions within the city that attempt to
resist Luda's soldiers, but it's such a nuisance. I keep
saying we should avoid pointless conflicts...

\N<Man>Protective armor can be considered the bare minimum of
preparation, whether exploring ruins or fighting in the
training grounds.

\N<Man>Protective armor can be considered the bare minimum of
preparation, whether you're exploring ruins or fighting in
the training grounds.
